faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身流鼻血以為自己鼻膜薄姐<br />\n點知依家呻鼻涕都有血絲"},{"pid":"0d387e0d4b2577222932893216226bd941b8cc87","tid":436020,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:10:55.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 傻閪"},{"pid":"dfd7900561c52e868c437ebefe27c9fbb0b5c6a9","tid":436020,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪鼻咽癌</blockquote><br />\n天氣乾燥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d3c6e5669cb0e7b818e62b23776110d520b6e","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦 傻閪</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母 最近幾好嗎"},{"pid":"c85742335e75fd38f4595552aa8a435534da839f","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪鼻咽癌</blockquote><br />\n天氣乾燥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17ec733d3ff0c1b17f0ece637ace225043d3473","tid":436020,"uid":44068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"鼻炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb5f3d66ab66e4912ecaaf6ca6e713282129347","tid":436020,"uid":115397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026c81c66409bd67a668ef4b2419f2cd0a7b5be3","tid":436020,"uid":148190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身流鼻血以為自己鼻膜薄姐<br />\n點知依家呻鼻涕都有血絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他症狀例如耳塞, 耳鳴, 頭痛, 淋巴腫撚咗嗰啲啊? 唔好太擔心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚就搵耳鼻喉專科啦, 多數一次過幫你用flexible laryngoscope照曬佢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1762b021776742ed30ce305b8f73323cd9cca42d","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會演變到cancer"},{"pid":"5b7a5dfd61f022beecbb112be00a773ad06819b7","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2285d9142d3dcb8dae9abe8a95472cb22961f93","tid":436020,"uid":25483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有鼻敏感 成日流鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次流左半個鐘未停<br />\n同事死都要幫我call白車<br />\n救護黎到自己都唔好意思<br />\n流鼻血咁小事都勞煩救護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係"},{"pid":"a6f98c9d805aef268a5081f34b914e04cdcbf116","tid":436020,"uid":70235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:26:53.000Z","msg":"之前我連續3日流鼻血，仲要隊埋酒都未死啦，唔使驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ddbecedf5c71fe17806bf407c092b31b1b48dd","tid":436020,"uid":103200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:32:13.000Z","msg":"流緊 瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8dcb53dd2cdaa6494d651d6f1ed312671c9c22","tid":436020,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身流鼻血以為自己鼻膜薄姐<br />\n點知依家呻鼻涕都有血絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他症狀例如耳塞, 耳鳴, 頭痛, 淋巴腫撚咗嗰啲啊? 唔好太擔心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚就搵耳鼻喉專科啦, 多數一次過幫你用flexible laryngoscope照曬佢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真答，鼻血只係其中一樣<br />\n要加埋喉嚨痛，淋巴腫先似<br />\n鼻塞鼻痛耳塞耳鳴加中耳炎同多痰都會有<br />\n可以去睇普通科醫生先，都係㩒下淋巴咁<br />\n<br />\n再唔放心就睇耳鼻喉科照鼻鏡，一眼睇唒鼻咽有冇事<br />\n再唔係就check埋DNA睇下有冇癌生長緊，99.9%準<br />\n利申之前都以為自己中招，最後原來係鼻敏感加鼻甲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b9c9fbc2a37c55c7eef5f7d34916f92af9f025","tid":436020,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:43:44.000Z","msg":"我年年冬天都會流 睇過醫生照左鏡話係鼻敏感問題 好難斷尾 只好保持鼻孔濕潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83115ae95603541dd7537cf75632c8916cf469e6","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我年年冬天都會流 睇過醫生照左鏡話係鼻敏感問題 好難斷尾 只好保持鼻孔濕潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係咁"},{"pid":"9e9c7388d98c6101db950224c5b533298caffe33","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身流鼻血以為自己鼻膜薄姐<br />\n點知依家呻鼻涕都有血絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他症狀例如耳塞, 耳鳴, 頭痛, 淋巴腫撚咗嗰啲啊? 唔好太擔心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚就搵耳鼻喉專科啦, 多數一次過幫你用flexible laryngoscope照曬佢㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真答，鼻血只係其中一樣<br />\n要加埋喉嚨痛，淋巴腫先似<br />\n鼻塞鼻痛耳塞耳鳴加中耳炎同多痰都會有<br />\n可以去睇普通科醫生先，都係㩒下淋巴咁<br />\n<br />\n再唔放心就睇耳鼻喉科照鼻鏡，一眼睇唒鼻咽有冇事<br />\n再唔係就check埋DNA睇下有冇癌生長緊，99.9%準<br />\n利申之前都以為自己中招，最後原來係鼻敏感加鼻甲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有頭痛無耳鳴耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8b32287f739a15d74e2ddd59d32f2d6c8fda9d","tid":436020,"uid":64578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:05:47.000Z","msg":"鼻黏膜薄所以容易流，血絲一條條果d通常都係鼻涕沾左血先咁樣，我以前有排都係咁，保持鼻哥濕潤，飲多d水，唔好捽咁大力"},{"pid":"37f62006f3e4ec9ee67f05438e9d61de93e9905e","tid":436020,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻黏膜薄所以容易流，血絲一條條果d通常都係鼻涕沾左血先咁樣，我以前有排都係咁，保持鼻哥濕潤，飲多d水，唔好捽咁大力</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45132a0abcc04dd22e20054a24b17339aa8d8631","tid":436020,"uid":628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:22:28.000Z","msg":"流緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}